Ding Baoyuan's area of activity,

565
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:11,960
and soon found out where he was.

566
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:18,510
Get him under control.

567
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,270
Don't move!

568
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:24,720
